    13,                           !- Minimum Cooling Supply Air Temperature {C}
    ,                             !- Maximum Heating Supply Air Humidity Ratio {kgWater/kgDryAir}
    ,                             !- Minimum Cooling Supply Air Humidity Ratio {kgWater/kgDryAir}
